{"tid":2404992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片］火炭警車讓路 俾非法賽車 同煙花車","createTime":"2021-02-12T05:15:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T06:23:46.000Z","uid":22556,"like":197,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"ded5a1a6f666fc054d26e18e006c2e56f676b801","tid":2404992,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T05:15:45.000Z","msg":"送鼠迎牛，處處喜氣洋洋。不過賀歲都要合法，賽車固然非法，放煙花助慶更加是罪加一等。網上流傳多條短片，顯示大年初一的凌晨時分，有近50部私家車在沙田火炭疑非法賽車，更以燒煙花做「起步禮」，場面相當誇張；即使警車見到，都要「讓路」。<br />\n<br />\n另一條車CAM所見，有車輛駛經火炭路山尾街交界時，有警車亮着藍燈在對面線出現，停在十字路口位，但沒有車輛因此減速或停下。一轉眼，車CAM所見，車輛已經駛出九龍，沿龍翔道往沙田方行駛，沿途高速左穿右插，即使有危險品車輛在旁，也切線爬頭，甚是危險。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210212/LNYELKY2FRDPPJ42IEZIAQHARI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210212%2FLNYELKY2FRDPPJ42IEZIAQHARI%2F&d=fMmZVRBh8JxXvfCabRklGacrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=45c5fa4d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210212%2FLNYELKY2FRDPPJ42IEZIAQHARI%2F&h=c72b6447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210212/LNYELKY2FRDPPJ42IEZIAQHARI/</a>"},{"pid":"b32a191bcaa78f01bdba092ea34bde74e577fc8d","tid":2404992,"uid":144919,"like":120,"dislike":0,"score":120,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T05:16:36.000Z","msg":"欺善怕惡唔意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d620ff9bade473a3d6ce2bfd5cddc5e623843b7","tid":2404992,"uid":7369,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T05:17:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黑警杯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b36d952955f9d9346b29852d1a9280ac0f3f4d","tid":2404992,"uid":43809,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T05:19:42.000Z","msg":"自己人講呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ff24efae6437073d794a1dbf2f0f22f20a5b532","ti